Revision history for File-is

0.04    12 October 2017
    * author tests moved to xt/

0.03    14 Sep 2010
    * thesame() now also checks device number (thanks to Ronald Fischer)
    * thesame() throws an exception on MSWin32 (thanks to Ronald Fischer)

0.02    30 Jun 2010
    * fixed the test for operating systems that doesn't support (sym)links
    * removed dependency on Readonly
    * using confess for exceptions

0.01    Date/time
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

